        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "TRENDYGOLF Has You Covered",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At TRENDYGOLF, we've always believed golf and fashion should elevate each other and Jason Day in Malbon is proof that we're headed in the right direction. If you're ready to step outside the box, rethink your fit, and bring a little edge to your next round, we've got the pieces to help you do it.</p><p>Explore the latest from <strong>Malbon</strong>, <strong>J.Lindeberg</strong>, <strong>Manors Golf</strong>, and more. Because the future of golf style? It's bold. It's curated. And it's finally interesting.</p>"
          }
        }
